sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant Gateway as RHOAI Gateway<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant HTTP as caikit-nlp HTTP<br/>8080/TCP Configurable TLS
    participant GRPC as caikit-nlp gRPC<br/>8085/TCP Configurable mTLS
    participant TGIS as TGIS Server<br/>gRPC Configurable mTLS
    participant Model as Local Model<br/>(in-memory)
    participant HF as HuggingFace Hub<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

    Note over Client,HF: Flow 1: HTTP Text Generation (Remote via TGIS)
    Client->>Gateway: POST /api/v1/task/text-generation<br/>Auth: Bearer Token / OAuth
    Gateway->>HTTP: Forward request<br/>8080/TCP, Configurable TLS
    HTTP->>TGIS: gRPC inference call<br/>Configurable mTLS
    TGIS-->>HTTP: Generated text response
    HTTP-->>Gateway: JSON response
    Gateway-->>Client: HTTPS response

    Note over Client,HF: Flow 2: gRPC Text Generation (Remote via TGIS)
    Client->>Gateway: gRPC TextGenerationTask<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    Gateway->>GRPC: Forward gRPC<br/>8085/TCP, Configurable mTLS
    GRPC->>TGIS: gRPC inference call<br/>Configurable mTLS
    TGIS-->>GRPC: Generated text response
    GRPC-->>Gateway: gRPC response
    Gateway-->>Client: gRPC response

    Note over Client,HF: Flow 3: Embedding / Reranking (Local Model)
    Client->>Gateway: POST /api/v1/task/embedding<br/>Auth: Bearer Token / OAuth
    Gateway->>HTTP: Forward request<br/>8080/TCP, Configurable TLS
    HTTP->>Model: Local inference<br/>(sentence-transformers)
    Model-->>HTTP: Embedding vectors
    HTTP-->>Gateway: JSON response
    Gateway-->>Client: HTTPS response

    Note over Client,HF: Flow 4: Model Bootstrapping (Startup)
    HTTP->>HF: GET model artifacts<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: HF Token (optional)
    HF-->>HTTP: Model weights & config
    HTTP->>Model: Load into memory
